BasicsOfCodingJavaScript
Author: Jon Marcum

This project is a JavaScript port of lesson content originally created by
Mark McGranaghan as part of the Go by Example project:
  https://github.com/mmcgrana/gobyexample

The Go by Example content is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution
3.0 Unported License:
  http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

Lesson content in this repository (source code and Markdown files) has been
adapted from Go by Example for comparative programming language study,
examining syntax, language simplicity, lines of code, and compile/run
performance across multiple languages. The Go reference implementation used
as the basis for this port is:
  https://github.com/jrmarcum/BasicsOfCodingGo

